The main goal on this project was to know what is the percentage of native trees vs exotic trees (not from Brazil) used in the city's urban forestry
to better understand, if and how native trees are taken into consideration when planting and planning the urban forestry.
I donwloaded the data from the city hall website and imported to the SQL Server

	
	
	Created a global temporary table to avoid modifying the original version of it, and called ## tree_record.
While doing that I only selected the columns I intend to use for this project and renamed them into international readible name for all columns.

	



